{"tid":1014514,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《銀河守護隊》火箭浣熊因病過世　享年9歲10個月","createTime":"2019-02-09T09:07:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-10T14:07:41.000Z","uid":39464,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"fbe2f26202543062ec541501dbaebf6c068a98a2","tid":1014514,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T09:07:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190209/640_9375d01749a841805b9ade15a314c96e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190209%2F640_9375d01749a841805b9ade15a314c96e.jpg&h=863d2533&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在漫威超級英雄電影《星際異攻隊》（Guardians of the Galaxy）中，「飾演」火箭浣熊的動物明星「奧利奧」（Oreo）周四（7日）因病去世，享年9歲10個月。<br />\n<br />\n火箭浣熊是漫威電影宇宙中，最受歡迎角色之一，除了有好萊塢前「性感王」布萊利庫柏（Bradley Cooper）的配音加持，在劇中嘴砲狂開；牠的造型設計也經過篩選，角色原型並非普通浣熊，而是找來一隻名叫奧利奧的浣熊作模特兒。<br />\n<br />\n負責照顧奧利奧的團體「Quinta Layla」表示，奧利奧於數天前突然發病，周四早上去世，走得很安詳。Quinta Layla又稱讚，奧利奧生前成為浣熊界的大使，帶給很多人快樂，且愛所有人，無論是好萊塢紅地毯、探訪兒童病院，還是任何挑戰，牠都一樣享受。<br />\n<br />\nQuinta Layla也分享10年前收養奧利奧的過程，憶述當年（2009年4月13日）在倫敦戲院接到電話，得知有小浣熊出生，於是馬上趕到牠身邊。當時牠的母親因為無法順利排出母乳，奧利奧是靠著人工哺育養大。雖然希望奧利奧能長命百歲，但也不希望牠像過去幾天那樣一直受苦，Quinta Layla強調會永遠懷念牠。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190209/640_d4e2119162f2e8249fd87101d7160331.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190209%2F640_d4e2119162f2e8249fd87101d7160331.jpg&h=15e951c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/ca/realtime/20190209/1514465/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fca%2Frealtime%2F20190209%2F1514465%2F&d=6BLFUKkZTytPAocRz50jIwESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=625ec609\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fca%2Frealtime%2F20190209%2F1514465%2F&h=8d6ccef1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/ca/realtime/20190209/1514465/</a>"},{"pid":"214f12b12c1fd7d69545d2e26d8a725bdd881f89","tid":1014514,"uid":182930,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T10:04:15.000Z","msg":"化灰啫"},{"pid":"5de9a0a6cdc91a0e20bdc3819cee22271a3858a5","tid":1014514,"uid":49151,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T15:29:10.000Z","msg":"是但搵另一隻都冇人知啦屌"},{"pid":"1112acd024a170de6031eff78aa70dcc26ceeb9c","tid":1014514,"uid":226155,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T15:41:44.000Z","msg":"成隊cast散曬"},{"pid":"2600d85cf750c21e320067cb5ab353746be24cea","tid":1014514,"uid":49044,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T15:45:06.000Z","msg":"屌你老母無james gunn嘅gotg根本就無可能揾得番果種味道<br />\nTaika Waititi 都係咁話"},{"pid":"328b7e170b3b7528230923545368817f7eb35ddc","tid":1014514,"uid":160147,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T15:55:21.000Z","msg":"收到風 第4集會復活"},{"pid":"5fe61e42eeae701ecde6deb2e8e92b4f748b8c30","tid":1014514,"uid":26451,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T17:36:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"63fac5b4a797fd7b074e46e1519e865037f769ee","tid":1014514,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fe61e42eeae701ecde6deb2e8e92b4f748b8c30","tid":1014514,"uid":26451,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T17:36:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T17:37:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"109ebbe6d19e5e236148ddc7b01d951ff851cd1e","tid":1014514,"uid":141577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"328b7e170b3b7528230923545368817f7eb35ddc","tid":1014514,"uid":160147,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T15:55:21.000Z","msg":"收到風 第4集會復活"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T04:05:27.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3024b1fd6111e6e566847ad